text: Sydney Football Club may refer to the following clubs based in Sydney, Australia. These clubs which bear the city's name participate in distinct codes of football. *Sydney FC, a soccer (association football) club *Sydney Roosters, a rugby league club *Sydney Swans, an Australian rules football club *a defunct rugby union club, formed in 1865 *Sydney Football Club (NSWAFL), an Australian rules football club formed in 1881 and closed in 1954
title: Sydney Football Club
